|dead-url= yes 
}}{{fr}}</ref>其中央掃描引擎成功通過了[[ICSA實驗室|ICSA實驗室]][[認證|認證]]以及[[西海岸實驗室|西海岸實驗室]]的測試過程，<ref>{{Cite web
 |url         = http://www.westcoastlabs.com/checkmark/productList/index.cfm?advanced=false&searchString=avast
 |title       = West Coast Labs Checkmark – Antivirus Certification
 |publisher   = 西海岸實驗室
